                h3 6. Qualitative - Survey
                p
                    | I also carried out a simple survey that asked people to rank the most popular filter criteria according to their preferences. For each one of them, I calculated its average and standard deviation from the ranking scores. Therefore, by picking ones with higher mean and lower standard deviation, I identified the most important and convincing decision factors—location, budget, ratings, and reviews.
