                    h3 3. Overfiltering
                    p I found that the more I encouraged customers to use filter in an effective and efficient way, the more they would encounter zero-result situations, where the empty state of search results kicked in.
                    p We believe that instead of preventing overfiltering, a better solution is to build an informative, robust and scalable empty state as it ensures more flexibility and better guidance to customers. When users are getting 0 matching properties,
